<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Donate to Help Save Lives</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
        }
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            background-image: url('https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5b5a266fcef372310148d6d6/1567460209464-IYTINWBNI8U2K1HNM2YY/20181225_165049%2B%25281%2529.jpg?format=2500w');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .hero-text {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }
        .donation-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }
        .donate-button {
            background-color: #2d8f5e;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .donate-button:hover {
            background-color: #24724b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">DONATE TO HELP SAVE LIVES</div>
        <div class="donation-message">
            Your donation of $30 provides one vest that will help keep a homeless person warmer in the freezing cold.
        </div>
        <form action="/donate" method="POST">
            <button type="submit" class="donate-button">Donate $30</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
